%N A395280 a(n) = Product_{k=1..n-2} (n*k + n - 1)! / (n*k + 1)!.
%C A395280 Product of the entries not on the border of an n X n square array with elements 1..n^2 listed in increasing order by rows (or 1 where no such entries exist). [See example]
%F A395280 a(n) = (n^2-n+1) * (n^2-n)! / (n^(2*n-4) * (n!)^2 * Pochhammer(1+1/n,n-1)).
%F A395280 a(n) ~ n^(2*n^2 - 7*n + 13/2) / (2*Pi * exp(n^2 - 3*n - 1/2)). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Apr 18 2026
%e A395280                                                          [1   2  3  4  5]
